defaultTA staff currently provide extensive support for customers in 
defaultclaiming housing costs via Housing Benefit to ensure income is secured, which includes maintaining a good working relationship with the council’s Revenues and Benefits department. This relationship is not likely to be possible as support for housing costs 
defaultmove under the DWP, especially where the customer is hard to engage and has not given consent to discuss their application. This may lead to delays in rental costs being paid
